title: A Well Packed Pack of Fruity Sample Packs
description:
The pack includes:

[FL SAMPLES]GAB STABS.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Korg KPR-77.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Yamaha EX7 Bass.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Techno Pack.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Funky.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Tekno.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Trends.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Extra2.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Extra Bass.exe
[FL SAMPLES]PRO DJ Delux Collection Extra Piano.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Voice Pack.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Pack Release 2.exe
[FL SAMPLES]Voice Pack (INPC).zip

They may be dated by now but there are still about 450 samples in there. I still love the Korg one-shots after all these years!!
They are Archive exes so you should be able to 'unpack' the whole lot to one folder in one go, point FL to the folder and Bobs you uncle ! :)
